            </origination>
        </did>
        <custodhist id="ref4">
            <head>Provenance</head>
            <p>The Seymour Herman Workoff Collection was donated to the Abraham Lincoln Brigade Archives by Irving Workoff, in 1975. This collection came to New York University in January 2001 as part of the original acquisition of ALBA collections, formerly housed at Brandeis University.</p>
